node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on September 17, 2021 tagging @anxietyhealer. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'casey @caseyyrose Someone who drowns in 7 feet of water is just as dead as someone who drowns in 20 feet of water. Stop comparing traumas stop belittling your or anyone else's trauma because it wasn't "as bad" as someone else's. This isn't a competition, we all deserve support and recovery.'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on September 16, 2021 tagging @anxietyhealer. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'feelingsarehar3 You are not behind in life. There's no timetable that we all must follow. It's made up. 7 billion people can't do everything in the same order. What's early? What's late? Compared to who? Don't beat yourself up for where you are. It's YOUR schedule and everything is right on time.'.

Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on September 11, 2021 tagging @lizandmollie, and @anxietyhealer. May be an image of text that says 'HOW WE THINK LIFE WORKS FINISH HWCTUALLY IT ACTUALLY WORKS FINISH START START LIZ @LIZ ANDMOLLIE'.

Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on September 11, 2021 tagging @anxietyhealer, and @allyse_has_anxiety. May be an image of text that says 'SYMPTOMS OF ANXIETY WE DON'T TALK ABOUT ENOUGH @ALLYSE_H HAS_ANXIETY'.

Photo by Anxiety Healer on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text.
Photo by Anxiety Healer on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Physical pain (in your chest, back, arms, legs) @ALLYSE_HAS_ANXIETY ANXIETY'.
Photo by Anxiety Healer on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Sleeping patterns that are so irregular you are constantly exhausted @ALLYSE_HAS_ANXIETY'.
Photo by Anxiety Healer on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Anxiety Healer on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'A generally higher resting heart rate @ALLYSE_HAS_ANXIETY'.
Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on September 11, 2021 tagging @anxietyhealer. May be an image of text that says 'Constant light headed feeling @ALLYSE_HA ANXIETY'.

Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on September 02, 2021 tagging @anxietyhealer, and @theopeninvite. May be an image of outdoors, tree and text that says 'PLEASE LOVE YOURSELF INSTEAD OF LOVING THE IDEA OF LOVING PEOPLE OTHER YOU THEOPENINVITE THEOPENINVITE'.

Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on August 27, 2021 tagging @ocdrecoveryuk. May be an image of text that says 'ROBERT BRAY Robert Bray @ocdrecovery Once I saw OCD was just a fear cycle I felt a weight off my shoulders, unti that point believed it was some indestructible like force.'.

Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on August 23, 2021 tagging @anxietyhealer, and @anxiousidiot. May be a meme of 2 people, beard and text that says '"I never would have thought you had anxiety, you seem so chill!" An seem relaxed, incredibly tense at all times.'.

Photo by Anxiety Healer on August 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'AITING Sinclair P. Ceasar III @Sinclair_Ceasar My therapist taught me to interrupt my anxious thinking with thoughts like: "What if things work out" and "What if all my hard work pays off?" So, I'm passing that onto you wherever you are, whatever you're leaving, or whomever you're becoming.'.

Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on August 15, 2021 tagging @anxietyhealer, and @regen_health. May be an image of text that says 'honeybee @punkmom_ Just a friendly reminder that anxiety attacks aren't always hyperventilating rocking back and forth. They are also random bursts of irritability ·obsessive behavior and nit picking hypersensitivity .pacing .silence .zoning out Always look for signs with your loved ones 12/9/17, 2:41 PM'.

node.text:
Mental illness, depression, and anxiety look different on everyone. Check on your people's regards of how “put together” they may seem. Remember that even if people don’t seem to be in distress on the outside, believe them, if they say they are.
Repost via @regen_health
📷 Credits punkmom_ on twitter

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on August 14, 2021 tagging @anxietyhealer. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'A$AP @asapsmoke01 "You're overthinking this" bro i have anxiety. have no other type of thinking available'.

Photo shared by Anxiety Healer on August 13, 2021 tagging @michellcclark, and @anxietyhealer. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'love yo self. @MichellCClark when was the last time you sat and gave yourself credit for how much you've grown and how far you've come? when was the last time you celebrated a relatively small win, just because? when was the last time you just sat down and said out loud, "I'm really really proud of myself?"'.
